{"tid":1501700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黑警還眼] 又爆眼？825全民入機場","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T08:11:40.000Z","uid":19926,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0e04f87a76fe3da9a4ed9b31d9004ce28b244707","tid":1501700,"uid":19926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:24:40.000Z","msg":"見Post者開新Post洗連登，重現812<br />\n<br />\n唔理825有咩活動，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日11am起一律入機場，勢要塞爆機場！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你仲有良心，有些少良知，唔理你和理非定勇武，825你一定要出現，為我哋嘅手足討回公道。香港人已經唔可以再俾警察恰到上心口。眼又爆，腳又斷，下一步就係手足斷送生命！<br />\n<br />\n係警察迫香港人，呢班警察為人工福利，不講仁義道德，迫香港上絕路。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">825唔塞爆機場，誓不為香港人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今次核爆都唔離開機場<br />\n因為香港人已經冇路走<br />\n行入機場，你有本事就打橫抬我哋出嚟</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油，機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n限時機場公海Link：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=293e5ef1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/walkin_airport_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwalkin_airport_news&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=f734901a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/walkin_airport_news</a>"},{"pid":"4e334b8632b08cdcd7fd4e7e0c88b537cf002495","tid":1501700,"uid":52090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:26:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日核彈</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[時事台重開]【是日核彈】【斷正】監控燈柱解剖 直通大陸 證據確鑿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1501550/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blan